Touch free operations, Open, close, seal the trash using Alexa voice.
(1) Download our “omo home” app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in our “omo home” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4) Search “omo home” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5) Enable “omo home” skill, and you'll be navigated to “omo home” login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
"Alexa, Open lid"
"Alexa, Close lid"
